name: Kagutsuchi (火之迦具土)
description: Kagutsuchi is the son of Izanagi who in the process of giving birth burned Izanami's mother to death. With deep sorrow for the loss of his wife, Izanagi beheaded Kagutsuchi and divided him into eight pieces with his sword. And then those eight parts became a volcano. As well as the blood that dripped through Izanagi's sword and then turned into several god figures.
